# Compose template and pre-launch script for the miner workload.
# - docker-compose.yaml: references the miner image by digest;
#   `gmcli deploy` renders ${GM_IMAGE_REF} and submits it to Phala Cloud.
# - prelaunch.sh: corrected Phala Cloud pre-launch script (digest-aware
#   GHCR ref parsing); `gmcli deploy` passes it via --pre-launch-script.
